reviews.review_text: GD @ Illinois U. Great matrix recording.  Nice work adding an audience patch on last 4 tracks to make a complete show.  Crisp sound.  Especially enjoyed "Passenger" and the "Lost Sailor/Saint Of Circumstance!"  Thanks for posting!
